{
  "stem": "19939.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had an ID.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I didn't say anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it didn't correspond exactly with what it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And through my stay there-- first of all the fear of being recognized, always alert, always listening to people who is coming and who is going, or who is something, knowing what to say.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were instances that I thought that's it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They required ration, food rations, for the workers, too, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In order to get these workers, you had to be, to be registered, right, and the [NON-ENGLISH], where the salt mines were.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the following day, said, you have to bring your ration something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have to be rationed, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we ate in this canteen without the rations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is every week, every few days, this is the end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is the end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is 1943.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I, I-- at night, I was praying to my-- this beloved grandmother-- not God, no [INAUDIBLE], help me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Help me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The following day came the pay master, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he brought-- we were like three or something, four.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he brought these four rations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he gave it to the, the chef, and mine including.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How, why he did it and how it happened, maybe he knew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I couldn't go to ask for this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then it started, you know-- I've heard what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the lagers, they started shooting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I spoke German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Came a, an SS, you know, Miller.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know his name was Miller.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was like this from the like this get from another camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
